    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1902-09-04T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1902-09-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="832"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d832">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Calderon</persName> to <gloss
                            type="to">Acting Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peruvian Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Gloucester, Mass.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-09-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 4, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>While deeply deploring the accident met with by His Excellency President
                    Roosevelt, I beg you to convey to him the hearty congratulations of the
                    President and the people of Peru, as well as my own, for his felicitious
                    escape.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Manuel Alvarez Calderon.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
